  {
    "id": "h013",
    "group": "config-gen",
    "prompt": "A solo developer wants to optimize their skill while working \u2014 each real task they do becomes training data. They want to review each gate decision manually before it's applied. What values should feedback_source and feedback_timing have, and why can't this work with parallelism > 1?",
